# MeshCore channel decryption keys
# Copy-paste the output of 'get_channels' from meshcore-cli directly, e.g.:
#
#   sam-g2|*> get_channels
#   0: Public [8b3387e9c5cdea6ac9e5edbaa115cd72]
#   1: #wardriving [e3c26491e9cd321e3a6be50d57d54acf]
#   2: #chaosstuff [b53025e867806e0b5e241adc0d47358b]
#
# Hashtag channels may also be listed without a key (key derived automatically):
#   #mynewchannel
#
# Lines starting with "# " are comments. Blank lines are ignored.
# Copy this file to channels.txt (gitignored) and edit for your setup.

# Paste your get_channels output below:
# 0: Public [8b3387e9c5cdea6ac9e5edbaa115cd72]
# 1: #yourhashtagchannel [xxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxxx]
